#: ../../B/Black-Screen-of-Death.rst:5
msgid "Black Screen of Death"
msgstr "Black Screen of Death"

#: ../../B/Black-Screen-of-Death.rst:9
msgid ""
"[prob. : related to the Floating Head of Death in a famous *Far Side* "
"cartoon.] A failure mode of :ref:`Microsloth-Windows`\\. On an attempt to "
"launch a DOS box, a networked Windows system not uncommonly blanks the "
"screen and locks up the PC so hard that it requires a cold :ref:`boot` to "
"recover. This unhappy phenomenon is known as The Black Screen of Death. See "
"also :ref:`Blue-Screen-of-Death`\\, which has become rather more common."
msgstr ""
"[おそらく、有名な\\ *Far Side*\\ の漫画に出てくるFloating Head of Death(浮かぶ死の頭)に関連]\\ "
":ref:`Microsloth-Windows`\\ "
"の故障モードの一つ。DOSボックスを起動しようとすると、ネットワーク接続されたWindowsシステムは、珍しくもなく画面を真っ暗にし、コールド\\ "
":ref:`boot`\\ でしか回復できないほど深くPCをロックする。この不幸な現象はThe Black Screen of "
"Deathとして知られる。より一般的になった\\ :ref:`Blue-Screen-of-Death`\\ も参照。"
